# LicenseGate Compatibility

### Verify via GET
GET {{baseUrl}}/license/{{userId}}/{{activationCode}}/verify
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}

###

### Verify via GET with challenge
GET {{baseUrl}}/license/{{userId}}/{{activationCode}}/verify?challenge=random-challenge-string
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}

###

### Verify via POST
POST {{baseUrl}}/license/{{userId}}/{{activationCode}}/verify
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "scope": "feature:premium",
  "challenge": "random-challenge-string"
}

###